ui.rules_title=SERVER RULES
ui.rules_blackbg1=The rules on this server must be strictly followed for the proper functioning of the server and coexistence with other players.\n\n\n
ui.rules_blackbg2=§l§c1)§r You are on a §l§cnon-Vanilla§r server, which means that the server's (physical) resources are dedicated and exclusive to these custom features. Therefore, building resource-intensive farms is prohibited. Constructing farms in private locations (houses) or in unprotected areas (Outer World, Nether, or End) will result in a temporary ban. Persistence may lead to the player's expulsion.\n\n
ui.rules_blackbg3=§l§c2)§r Exploiting game weaknesses or glitches for personal advantage is not allowed. Knowledge of any weakness without reporting it to Moderators/Game Masters may also be considered an infraction.\n\n
ui.rules_blackbg4=§l§c3)§r Destroying and/or modifying existing builds on the server is not permitted. If you wish to make any changes, please contact one of the Moderators of the respective city.\n\n
ui.rules_blackbg5=§l§c4)§r Unjustified and mass player killing may result in your user account being banned for a specified period. Repeated offenses may lead to the player's expulsion.\n\n
ui.rules_blackbg6=§l§c5)§r Any form of insult, slander, or hate speech is prohibited and may result in the player's expulsion.\n\n
ui.rules_blackbg7=§l§c6)§r Providing false information or false reports to Moderators/Game Masters is prohibited and may result in a temporary ban of your user account.\n\n
ui.rules_blackbg8=§l§c7)§r Builds within cities must adhere to the theme of the respective city. Failure to follow the established standard may result in the loss of your house and/or plot.\n\n
ui.rules_blackbg9=§l§c8)§r Attempting to violate or violating the rules described here may result in a temporary ban. Serious cases will be evaluated by the Moderation/Game Master team and may lead to the player's expulsion.\n\n

