system.npc.bank_welcome=Welcome to the central bank of §l§e%2§r!\n\nHere I can help you with withdrawals and deposits.\n§lHow can I assist you?
system.npc.fairy_dust_welcome=Hello! Would you like to buy some Banking Fairy Dust?\n\nIt can be very useful in your adventures to perform certain financial operations.
system.npc.blacksmith_welcome=Hello, I am §l§e%1§r from §l§e%2§r. I can repair any equipment, but don’t bring me things that aren’t worth my time.\n\n§lDo you have something to repair?
system.npc.blacksmith_shop_welcome=Hello, I am §l§e%1§r and here in §l§e%2§r we have the best blacksmith in all of Inner! I sell equipment crafted by him. Want to take a look?\n\nWe also buy items. Some can be reused, resold, or even melted down to create new equipment. §lDo you have anything interesting?§r
system.npc.sailor_welcome=Welcome aboard, sailor!\n\nHow can I help you?
system.npc.food_welcome=Welcome to the best kitchen in §l§e%2§r!\n\n§lWhat would you like to eat today?
system.npc.lodging_welcome=Hello, welcome!\n\nWould you like to stay the night?\nWe have §l§3Standard§r§f rooms for §l§3B$ 5§r§f or §l§6Presidential§r§f for §l§6B$ 20§r§f. Which would you prefer?
system.npc.magic_welcome=Hello, I am §l§e%1§r, Grand Master of the Magic Academy of §l§e%2§r.\n\nWould you like to learn something? It would be my pleasure to welcome another member into our world of magic!
system.npc.magic_supply_welcome=Hello adventurer, if you are looking for magical supplies I have what you need. Take a look at what I have here.


system.npc.king_welcome=The throne listens only to the worthy...\n\n§lWhat is your wish?
system.npc.king.promotion_requirements=§fNobility is not granted to the weak.\nOnly those who show courage and ambition may ascend.\n\n§fRequirements:\n  > Level 20+\n  > Chosen class\n  > Tribute of §l§6B$ 20,000§r§f to the Crown\n  > Be a Premium Account
system.npc.king.promotion_no_premium=<§l%1§r§f> You need an active premium account to access this service.
system.npc.king.promotion_not_met=<§l%1§r§f> You are not ready for nobility yet. Return once you meet all requirements.
system.npc.king.promotion_success=<§l%1§r§f> In the name of the kingdom, I now declare you a §l§n%2§r§f.
system.npc.king.promotion_no_balance=<§l%1§r§f> You do not have enough funds to pay the tribute. Return once you meet all requirements.
system.npc.king.already_promoted=<§l%1§r§f> You have already received your promotion.

system.npc.bank_first_money_welcome=§fHello!\nWelcome to the central bank of §l§6Inner World§r§f.\n\nIf you are new here, the bank can give you a little help to start your journey.\n\nI am not very good with faces, have you been here before?
