system.npc.monk_gyatso_welcome=§fHello, have you come seeking higher knowledge?\n\nI arrived here a long time ago. The great Oracle taught us much about life and the afterlife, and I can even touch the veil of eternity that divides both worlds.\n\nI can teach you something through the stones of eternity. Would you like to learn?
system.npc.monk_tenzi_welcome=§fHello, have you come seeking higher knowledge?\n\nI came from Béstamo, but this is my home now. The great Oracle allows us to stay, and we help maintain the temple. If you seek eternity, I know part of the Oracle's teachings.\n\nI can teach you something through the stones of eternity. Would you like to learn?
system.npc.monk_jamphel_welcome=§fHello, have you come seeking higher knowledge?\n\nIt seems the great Oracle already sensed your arrival. If you have come seeking eternal life, my knowledge is vague compared to the great Oracle's, but I can touch the veil of eternity and help you.\n\nI can teach you something through the stones of eternity. Would you like to learn?
system.npc.monk_yeshe_welcome=§fHello, have you come seeking higher knowledge?\n\nI came from beyond the colossal barriers. Here we live in peace thanks to the powers of the Gods of Inner.\nAnd with the help of the great Oracle, we learned much; I can even touch the veil of eternity.\n\nI can teach you something through the stones of eternity. Would you like to learn?

system.npc.monk_farewell=May the light of the Gods of Inner guide your path.
system.npc.monk_cancel=I understand. Return when you feel the time is right.
system.npc.monk_bless_desc=§fWith the protection of this stone, you will reduce by §l§n25%%%§r§f the amount of experience you would lose.\n\nCost: §l§aB$ 10,000§r§f\n\nDo you wish to receive this bless?

system.npc.monk_already_blessed=§l§cYou have already been protected by my energy before...
system.npc.monk_bless_granted=§l§6By the powers of the Gods of Inner...\nYou will be protected from now on!

system.npc.label.time_stone=Time Stone
system.npc.label.end_stone=End Stone
system.npc.label.sun_stone=Sun Stone
system.npc.label.soul_stone=Soul Stone



system.npc.monk_bhadrapala_welcome=§fWelcome, adventurer!\n\nIf you seek to protect your most valuable belongings, perhaps I can bind the energy of your spirit to the matter of your item. This will make your item follow you even into the spiritual plane.\n\nDid you bring something to bless?
system.npc.label.bless_item=Bless
system.npc.monk_item_no_item=§cYou have nothing I can bless. Come back when you have something.
system.npc.monk_item_already_blessed=§cThis item already has a spiritual bond.
system.npc.monk_item_bless_granted=§fHere it is! Your item now has a spiritual bond with you.
system.npc.monk_item_bless_desc=§fItem: §l§e%1§r§f\n\nI can bind the energy of your spirit to this item, making it follow you even into the spiritual plane.\n\nCost: §l§aB$ %2§r§f\n\nDo you wish to bless this item?

system.npc.monk_bufang_welcome=§fHello, I am Bufang, the first priest of this path.\n\nFrom this point onward, your steps will touch the borders of the spiritual world.\n\nIf your heart has already proven its worth, the great §l§3Oracle§r§f may grant what you deeply seek.
system.npc.monk_gyalwa_welcome=§fHello, traveler. Welcome to the §l§nTemple of Parnassus§r§f, home of the great §l§3Oracle§r§f.\n\nThis place is sacred, raised between the silence of stone and the harmony of the winds.\n\nWalk in peace, for not all knowledge must be sought in haste.
system.npc.monk_rinponche_welcome=§fMay the winds of Parnassus welcome your arrival, adventurer.\n\nYou stand before the §l§nTemple of Parnassus§r§f, where the great §l§3Oracle§r§f contemplates the echoes of life and eternity.\n\nRespect this sacred ground, and perhaps it will also respect your journey.
system.npc.monk_zhang_welcome=§fHello!\n\nHere in the §l§nTemple of Parnassus§r§f, home of the great §l§3Oracle§r§f, we learn that peace and war first dwell within ourselves.\n\nI am new here, but they say adventurers from every corner of the world come to this temple seeking eternal knowledge.


system.npc.tableville_grace_welcome=§fMy lips have a lot to say, but they prefer not to use words...
system.npc.tableville_mary_welcome=§fI don’t want trouble coming my way... unless the trouble is you.
system.npc.tableville_girls_farewell=Sure, come back whenever you want... and I know you want to.


system.npc.label.destinations=Destinations
system.npc.train_destination_desc==§fWhere would you like to travel?
system.npc.train_welcome=§fHello, welcome to the %1 train station.\n\nWould you like to buy a ticket today?
system.npc.train_farewell=Sure, come back whenever you need to travel.
system.npc.train_thanks=Thank you, and have a good trip!


system.npc.daryl_welcome=§fHello young one, I am only an old fisherman, but I have seen rare things in the waters and forests of Edelfia.\nOnce, I found a ruin deep in the forest, where the waters meet. You will know you have arrived when the path seems to end... from there, only the depths of your solitude may guide you. But do not lose your way: sometimes, light finds those who reach the end of the tunnel.\n\nAnd beware of the Orcs. Years ago, they invaded our forest and left scars that never healed.\nI saw one of their settlements in a cave to the southeast. You may find Goblins along the way... The forest keeps secrets, but not all of them wish to be found.


inner.classid.10.name=Newbie
inner.classid.10.promoted_name=Newbie
inner.classid.10.short_desc=You are a beginner, explore and look for a vocation that best fits you, or just keep being an ordinary citizen!
inner.classid.10.long_desc=""
inner.classid.11.name=Barbarian
inner.classid.11.promoted_name=Untamed Barbarian
inner.classid.11.short_desc=Fight in a wild way, with less refined combat technique.\nBarbarians have inner rage that lets them ignore some received blows.
inner.classid.11.long_desc=a fighter who battles fiercely, with less refined technique but extreme ferocity!\nBarbarians have an inner rage that lets them ignore some blows taken.\n\nPrimary Skill: §l§6Strength§r\nSecondary: §l§6Constitution§r
inner.classid.12.name=Bard
inner.classid.12.promoted_name=Virtuoso Bard
inner.classid.12.short_desc=A caster of inspiring, influencing and manipulating magic.\nThey use words and music to shape the minds of listeners.
inner.classid.12.long_desc=a caster of inspiring, influencing and manipulating magic.\nYou will use your words and songs to shape the minds of listeners.\n\nPrimary Skill: §l§6Charisma§r\nSecondary: §l§6Dexterity§r
inner.classid.13.name=Warlock
inner.classid.13.promoted_name=Arcane Warlock
inner.classid.13.short_desc=Casters with their own way of working, unlike other classes.\nThey draw power from pacts with ancient and mysterious beings.
inner.classid.13.long_desc=a caster with its own way of working, different from other classes.\nThey draw powers from pacts with ancient and mysterious creatures.\n\nPrimary Skill: §l§6Charisma§r\nSecondary: §l§6Wisdom§r
inner.classid.14.name=Cleric
inner.classid.14.promoted_name=High Cleric
inner.classid.14.short_desc=Casters who gain magic through prayers to deities.\nTheir faith and devotion are rewarded with special powers.
inner.classid.14.long_desc=a mediator between the mortal world and the distant realm of the gods.\nYou strive to be the very hand of your gods. Not just a common priest, but someone invested with divine power.\n\nPrimary Skill: §l§6Wisdom§r\nSecondary: §l§6Charisma§r
inner.classid.15.name=Druid
inner.classid.15.promoted_name=Elder Druid
inner.classid.15.short_desc=Magic casters tied to the elemental forces of nature.\nThey are the active arm of the wild world against its foes.
inner.classid.15.long_desc=a magic caster linked to the elemental forces of nature.\nYour spells focus on nature and animals, the power of claws, sun and moon, fire and storm.\n\nPrimary Skill: §l§6Wisdom§r\nSecondary: §l§6Intelligence§r
inner.classid.16.name=Sorcerer
inner.classid.16.promoted_name=Supreme Sorcerer
inner.classid.16.short_desc=Casters whose bloodline links them to magical creatures, or supernatural events that granted them power.
inner.classid.16.long_desc=a caster carrying magical heritage granted to you by an exotic lineage, some otherworldly influence, or exposure to unknown cosmic forces.\n\nPrimary Skill: §l§6Charisma§r\nSecondary: §l§6Constitution§r
inner.classid.17.name=Ranger
inner.classid.17.promoted_name=Celestial Ranger
inner.classid.17.short_desc=Relentless fighters and vigilant guardians of uncharted lands and the world.\nThey combine speed, stealth, and precision.
inner.classid.17.long_desc=a vigilant fighter of the uncharted lands and the world, with unmatched mastery of weapons and armor at any range, with incredible skill and precision in combat.\n\nPrimary Skills: §l§6Dexterity & Wisdom§r\nSecondary: §l§6Strength§r
inner.classid.18.name=Warrior
inner.classid.18.promoted_name=Elite Warrior
inner.classid.18.short_desc=Masters of combat techniques, with unmatched mastery of weapons and armor, excelling in the art of war.
inner.classid.18.long_desc=a fighter mastering combat techniques with unmatched skill in weapons and armor, excelling in the art of war. You will learn the basics of every combat style.\n\nPrimary Skills: §l§6Strength & Dexterity§r\nSecondary: §l§6Constitution§r
inner.classid.19.name=Rogue
inner.classid.19.promoted_name=Phantom Rogue
inner.classid.19.short_desc=Masters of skills and tools for worldly abilities.\nThey use stealthy means to match their foes.
inner.classid.19.long_desc=a master of skills and tools for worldly abilities, focusing on stealth and refining your skills to aid in dungeons.\nYou will use stealthy means to match your enemies.\n\nPrimary Skill: §l§6Dexterity§r\nSecondary: §l§6Intelligence§r
inner.classid.20.name=Wizard
inner.classid.20.promoted_name=Archmage
inner.classid.20.short_desc=Scholarly casters seeking magical and supernatural knowledge, using study to wield and improve magic.
inner.classid.20.long_desc=a scholarly caster seeking magical and supernatural knowledge.\nUsing the subtle weave of magic that permeates the cosmos, you will cast powerful spells, subtle deceptions, and control minds with brute force.\n\nPrimary Skill: §l§6Intelligence§r\nSecondary: §l§6Wisdom§r
inner.classid.21.name=Monk
inner.classid.21.promoted_name=Exalted Monk
inner.classid.21.short_desc=Disciplined fighters, studying movement and energy flowing within themselves and others.\nThey know the mystical energy within everyone.
inner.classid.21.long_desc=a disciplined fighter, student of movement and the energy flowing within yourself. Whatever your discipline, you share the ability to magically harness the energy flowing in your body.\n\nPrimary Skills: §l§6Dexterity & Wisdom§r\nSecondary: §l§6Strength§r
inner.classid.22.name=Paladin
inner.classid.22.promoted_name=Royal Paladin
inner.classid.22.short_desc=Fighters who faithfully follow an oath sworn to fight evil.\nArmed with combat skills and powers from their sacred vow.
inner.classid.22.long_desc=a fighter who faithfully follows an oath sworn to face evil.\nArmed with combat skills and powers from your sacred oath.\n\nPrimary Skills: §l§6Strength & Charisma§r\nSecondary: §l§6Wisdom§r
