ui.oracle.title=§l§6The Oracle§r
ui.oracle.dialog.1=§fWho dares to dive into my tears?\nI am §l§6The Oracle§r§f, I have been here since the dawn of time, linked to the spiritual world and the Gods of Inner, I foresaw apocalyptic wars and devastating events, great kings once sought my wisdom... \nAnd you? What do you seek?
ui.oracle.dialog.2=You are still young and have much to learn, yet I can help awaken your senses, but know this is irreversible, once the choice is made you cannot return.\n\nAre you certain of this?..
ui.oracle.dialog.3=§fAnd which vocation speaks to you the most? Answer wisely, and remember this choice cannot be undone.
ui.oracle.dialog.4=You chose to become a §l§6%1§r, you shall become %2
ui.oracle.button.1=§fAwaken my power...
ui.oracle.button.2=§fYes, I'm sure.
ui.oracle.button.3=§l§fYes!
ui.oracle.button.4=§l§cNo
ui.oracle.dialog.final=§l§6So it shall be done...



