############################
## The Elven Scissors ##
############################

## NPC Settings
system.npc.valvyre.welcome=Hello! Welcome to my collection! How can I help you?

system.quest.3.name=The Elven Scissors
system.quest.3.description=Valvyre is desperately looking for his scissors. It seems the orcs have hidden them somewhere, but I do not know where... I need to investigate the surroundings.

## Root button return messages
system.quest.3.msg.welcome.0=I am sorry, adventurer, but I no longer have the spirit to craft anything. Without my magical scissors, I am nothing but a mere mortal...

system.quest.3.msg.in_progress=Thank you, adventurer. I am eager to see you triumph! Bring me my magical scissors and you will be rewarded!
system.quest.3.msg.complete=I expected nothing less from you, great adventurer! Thank you!\n\nNow I can return to my majestic craftsmanship.
system.quest.3.msg.no_item=I thought you had it, please come back with my precious...

## Dialog messages
ui.quest.3.msg.1=Terrible news! During the last orc invasion, I lost my magical scissors, forged by the elven lord himself. Without them, I cannot make anything!
ui.quest.3.msg.2=If you could help me find them, I would be very grateful!\n\nDo you think you can help me?
ui.quest.3.msg.3=Thank you! Take this key. One of the orcs dropped it while they were looting my shop. It may be useful!
ui.quest.3.msg.4=What a wonderful surprise! In truth, I expected nothing less from you, great adventurer! Thank you! Now I can return to my majestic craftsmanship.\n\nHere, accept this as a reward!

## Quest log (check points)
system.quest.3.check_point.1=Valvyre lost his magical scissors, forged by the elven lord himself. Without them, he cannot make anything! They seem to be very special to him, and I feel obliged to help... After all, he has an excellent reputation in every city, and I really need some upgrades.
system.quest.3.check_point.2=I think I found Valvyre's scissors. He will be happy to have them back. As soon as I pass through Edélfia, I will pay him a visit.
system.quest.3.check_point.3=Valvyre was very happy to receive his scissors back. He gave me a saddle bag as a reward!\n\nBesides that, now that he is back to work, I can order something for myself!

## Valvyre Store (only on quest completion)
ui.quest.3.store.no_item=You don't have all necessary items or money for it, please return once you have all.
ui.quest.3.msg_accessories=I can craft some accessories. What do you need?


############################
## Galloping or Flying! ##
############################

## NPC Settings
system.npc.valvyre.welcome=Hello! Welcome, explorer! How can I help you?

system.quest.4.name=Galloping or Flying!
system.quest.4.description=I met Uncle Bill, and he seems to be very skilled with mounts. Maybe he can help me tame some!

## Root button return messages
system.quest.4.msg.welcome.0=I love Lady Bugs!\n\nTell me if you need anything else for mounts. I am willing to help!

system.quest.4.msg.in_progress=I see you have returned. Did you get the Broken Lady Bug Shells? If so, hand them over and I will be able to help you with them!
system.quest.4.msg.complete=What an achievement! How is your Lady Bug?
system.quest.4.msg.no_item=I thought you had it. Please come back when you have everything!

## Dialog messages
ui.quest.4.msg.1=I was young once, just like you, and believe me... Horses are not the only ones that need good riders.\nThere are many types of mounts in this world, but there is one in particular that excites me. Have you heard about the Lady Bugs found deep in the forest of Edélfia?\nThey are incredible! But do not be fooled, they are very fast and need a skilled rider to mount them!\n\nIf you can get some of the broken shells they leave behind, I can help you tame one!
ui.quest.4.msg.2=Deal! I will be happy to work with them again!
ui.quest.4.msg.3=Great! Thank you for this, and take it!\n\nWith this complete shell, you will be able to tame a Lady Bug, but be careful... They may not accept the gift and might even break it!

## Quest log (check points)
system.quest.4.check_point.1=Uncle Bill seems excited when he talks about these Lady Bugs. I hope I can find what he is looking for, and maybe I can get a new mount... I need 250x Broken Lady Bug Shells.
system.quest.4.check_point.2=I think I gathered enough for Uncle Bill, and he gave me a complete shell. Now I can tame Lady Bugs, and it seems he is willing to help me with other mounts!

## Uncle Bill Store (only on quest completion)
ui.quest.4.store.no_item=You don't have all the necessary items or enough money for this. Come back when you have everything.
ui.quest.4.msg_accessories=I can make some accessories. What do you need?
ui.quest.4.msg_tame_items=I can forge some taming items. What do you need?

